'''尼魯佛·迪米爾'''（{{lang-tr|Nilüfer Demir}}, {{bd|1986年||}}）是[[土耳其人|土耳其]][[博德鲁姆|博德鲁姆]]的一名[[攝影記者|攝影記者]]和[[攝影師|攝影師]]。

==生平==
她十几岁起<ref name="cnn">{{cite web|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2015/09/03/world/dead-migrant-boy-beach-photographer-nilufer-demir/|title=Photographer describes 'scream' of migrant boy's 'silent body'|last=Giggs|first=Brandon|date=2015-09-03|publisher=CNN|accessdate=2015-09-10|archive-date=2015-09-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150908113002/http://edition.cnn.com/2015/09/03/world/dead-migrant-boy-beach-photographer-nilufer-demir/|dead-url=no}}</ref>就开始在[[多安通讯社|多安通讯社]]工作。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ad.nl/ad/nl/1013/Buitenland/article/detail/4135216/2015/09/03/Fotografe-over-peuter-Aylan-Ik-versteende-helemaal.dhtml|title=Fotografe over peuter Aylan: Ik versteende helemaal|last=van Ast|first=Maarten|date=2015-09-03|publisher=[[每日汇报|Ad.nl]]|language=nl|accessdate=2015-09-10|archive-date=2015-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150906223433/http://www.ad.nl/ad/nl/1013/Buitenland/article/detail/4135216/2015/09/03/Fotografe-over-peuter-Aylan-Ik-versteende-helemaal.dhtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>她在2015年夏天报道了[[欧洲移民危机|欧洲移民危机]]，她于2015年9月2日在博德鲁姆海滩上遇到了[[艾兰·库尔迪之死|艾兰·库尔迪]]的尸体，拍摄了几张照片,之后这几张照片成为世界各国媒体的头条新闻。<ref name="cnn" />她说，看到蹒跚学步孩子的尸体，她感到“惊呆了”。 然后她拍了照片分享她的感受。<ref>[http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/photographer-of-the-world-shaking-picture-of-drowned-syrian-toddler-i-was-petrified-at-that-moment.aspx?pageID=238&nid=87951&NewsCatID=341 "Photographer of the world-shaking picture of drowned Syrian toddler: 'I was petrified at that moment'".] {{Wayback|url=http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/photographer-of-the-world-shaking-picture-of-drowned-syrian-toddler-i-was-petrified-at-that-moment.aspx?pageID=238&nid=87951&NewsCatID=341 |date=20150907202552 }} {{link-en|自由每日新闻|Hürriyet Daily News}}。 2015-09-03。</ref><ref>Andrew Katz (2015-09-03)。 [https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/worldviews/wp/2015/09/03/photographer-who-found-syrian-toddler-dead-on-turkish-beach-i-was-petrified/ "Photographer who found Syrian toddler dead on Turkish beach: ‘I was petrified’".] {{Wayback|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/worldviews/wp/2015/09/03/photographer-who-found-syrian-toddler-dead-on-turkish-beach-i-was-petrified/ |date=20150906070200 }} [[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]]。</ref>

